\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Supplementary synthetic validation details. We report directed Chamfer Distance (CD) components: Ours-to-Ground-truth (O2G) and Ground-truth-to-Ours (G2O), along with the symmetric sum (Sym = O2G + G2O) and normalized value ($\mathrm  {CD}_{\text  {norm}}$). Absolute (mm) and relative (rel) temporal CD ($\Delta \mathrm  {CD}$) are shown. Point-cloud overlap metrics (Precision P, Recall R, F-score F) are reported across a sweep of proximity thresholds $\tau $. Ground-truth comparison metrics are reported at $\tau = \SI {1}{\milli \meter }$ by default.}}{1}{}\protected@file@percent }
